title: WallStreet
description: A Simple yet Stylish 💅🏼 wallpaper app made using Jetpack compose / Kotlin Multiplatform that support MacOS, Windows, Linux & Android (Hopefully IOS joins the train as well). Its Free, OpenSource, Ad-Free, Performant and you can add your own wallpaper collection (github.com/StarkDroid/WallStreet-API),
